From 40840afa53bed05b990b201d749dfee3bd6e7e42 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Benjamin Berg <benjamin.berg@intel.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Jun 2025 21:21:18 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: move dBm averaging function into utils
Git-commit: 40840afa53bed05b990b201d749dfee3bd6e7e42
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

The function really is just a simple math helper. Move it into
iwl-utils.c so that it can also be used by iwlmld.

Signed-off-by: Benjamin Berg <benjamin.berg@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250609211928.8cc965af6990.I09bb2137863e888efe756c92d8eb0271ec95456c@changeid
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

